Accounting Manager - Multinational Electrical Manufacturing
Responsibilities
Our respective client, a Multinational Electrical Manufacturing is looking for a potential candidate to fill Accounting Manager position in their organization. This role will be responsible on :Supervise and responsible on Internal audit, External audit and Tax audit.Leading accountant division and doing business analysisBookeeping, cost control and assist Finance Director in annual budgetting. Requirements: Preferably 40 - 45 years old, seniors are welcome to applyCandidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, Finance/Accountancy/Banking or equivalent.At least 8 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.Applicants must be willing to work in Cikarang.Preferably Manager specializing in Finance - General/Cost Accounting or equivalent.Full-Time position(s) available.
